1. *Dolaziš* li kod mene? (Are you coming to my place?)
2. *Dolazi* li tata? (Is dad coming?)
3. Ne znam da li *dolaziš* večeras. (I don't know if you're coming tonight.)
4. Ona *dolazi* u pet časova. (She is coming at five o'clock.)
5. *Dolazio* je svaki dan. (He was coming every day.)
6. *Dolazila* je često. (She was coming often.)
7. *Dolazi* li i tvoj brat? (Is your brother coming too?)
8. On se nije *dolazio* u poslednje vreme. (He hasn't been coming lately.)